long.ar,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_GB,en_US,es,es_4:
TG Content Downloader - Telegram Download Helper
The TG Content Downloader is a powerful tool that helps users easily download audio, video, and images from Telegram to their computers. With our plugin, you can freely save various content for personal or academic use. We recommend that users do not download copyrighted content without permission.

💥 Key Features 

☑️ One-Click Bulk or Single Download:
Easily select multiple files or download a single resource with one click, making the download process quick and smooth.

☑️ Wide Format Support:
Download multiple media formats, including videos, images, photos, GIFs, music, and audiobooks, all in one convenient tool.

☑️ Save Content from Restricted Channels and Groups:
Easily save audio and video files from restricted Telegram channels and groups directly to your local computer, ensuring you have access to all your favorite content.

☑️ Extract Private Content:
Securely save audio and video from private channels and personal shares.

☑️ No Password or API Required:
Simplify the user experience by starting downloads without entering any additional information.

☑️ 24/7 Support:
We provide round-the-clock technical support to resolve your usage issues.

☑️ Easily Download 1G+ Content

☑️ Comprehensive Compatibility:
Our Telegram video downloader supports both A and K versions of channels and groups, making it easy to access your favorite content.

Get Started with the Telegram Content Downloader:
💥 Install the Chrome Extension
💥 Pin the Extension:
In the upper right corner of your browser, click the “Extensions” button next to your profile icon.
Find the newly installed plugin and click the “Pin” icon on the right to pin it to your toolbar for quick access.

💥 Access Telegram Web:
Open the Telegram web version in your browser: https://web.telegram.org/k or https://web.telegram.org/a.

💥 Batch Download Chat Content:
Browse the chat content of the channel or group you wish to download from.
The extension icon in the toolbar will display the number of resources captured.
Click the extension icon in the toolbar to open the plugin window, select the desired content, and easily proceed with batch downloading.

💥 Batch Download Group Information Content:
Enter the channel or group you are interested in and view the group information.
Click the “Download All Media” or “Download This Month’s Media” button to quickly obtain all media files in the group.

💥 Single File Download:
In the chat window of the channel or group, you will see a “Download” button below each music file, audiobook, video, or image.
Click the “Download” button to quickly download individual files.

📝 Disclaimer:
This plugin is independently developed and is not affiliated with the official Telegram app or website. Please ensure compliance with relevant laws and regulations before use.

Open the Telegram web version in your browser: https://web.telegram.org/k or https://web.telegram.org/a.

💥 Single File Download:

Click the “Download” button to quickly download individual files.
